n, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "2nd_reading_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but not voting (second reading)", "description": "How many members were present at the vote in the bill's second reading in the chamber specified in 'enacted_by' or 'considered_by', but did not cast a vote. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "3rd_reading_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but not voting (third reading)", "description": "How many members were present at the vote in the bill's third reading in the chamber specified in 'enacted_by' or 'considered_by', but did not cast a vote. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "passed_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but not voting (passage without three readings)", "description": "How many members were present at the vote on the bill's passage in the chamber specified in 'enacted_by' or 'considered_by', but did not cast a vote, if that chamber does not pass bills in three readings.", "type": "number" }, "conf_committee_passed_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but not voting (conference committee)", "description": "How many members were present at the vote on the version of the bill adopted by the conference committee in the chamber specified in 'enacted_by' or 'considered_by', in jurisdictions that do this, but did not cast a vote. Omit if no vote was taken.", "type": "number" }, "amendments_considered_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but not voting (first chamber's final decision in an asymmetrical procedure)", "description": "In bicameral legislatures that use an asymmetrical legislative procedure, how many members were present at the vote on the first chamber's final decision on the bill, but did not cast a vote. Omit if no vote was taken.", "type": "number" }, "veto_override_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but