t if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "2nd_reading2_against": { "label": "Votes against (second reading; second chamber)", "description": "How many members voted against the bill in its second reading in the second chamber. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "3rd_reading2_against": { "label": "Votes against (third reading; second chamber)", "description": "How many members voted against the bill in its third reading in the second chamber. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "passed2_against": { "label": "Votes against (passage without three readings; second chamber)", "description": "How many members voted against the bill's passage in the second chamber, if that chamber does not pass bills in three readings.", "type": "number" }, "conf_committee_passed2_against": { "label": "Votes against (conference committee; second chamber)", "description": "How many members voted against the version of the bill adopted by the conference committee in the second chamber, in jurisdictions that do this. Omit if no vote was taken.", "type": "number" }, "veto_override2_against": { "label": "Votes against (veto override; second chamber)", "description": "How many members voted against overriding the bill's veto in the second chamber. Omit if no vote was taken.", "type": "number" }, "1st_reading2_abstention": { "label": "Votes to abstain (first reading; second chamber)", "description": "How many members voted to abstain (however called in the jurisdiction; e.g. 'present', 'blank vote') at the bill's first reading in the second chamber. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "2nd_reading2_abstention": { "label": "Votes to abstain (second reading; second chamber)", "description": "How many members voted to abstain (however called in the jurisdiction; e.g. 'present', 'blank vote') at the bill's second reading in the second chamber. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "3rd_reading2_abstention": { "label": "Votes to abstain (third reading; second chamber)", "description": "How many members voted to abstain (however called in the jurisdiction; e.g. 'present', 'blank vote') at the bill's third reading in the second chamber. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "passed2_abstention": { "label": "Votes to abstain (passage without three readings; second chamber)", "description": "How many members voted to abstain (however called in the jurisdiction; e.g. 'present', 'blank vote') at the vote on the bill's passage in the second chamber, if that chamber does not pass bills in three readings.", "type": "number" }, "conf_committee_passed2_abstention": { "label": "Votes to abstain (conference committee; second chamber)", "description": "How many members voted to abstain (however called in the jurisdiction; e.g. 'present', 'blank vote') at the vote on the version of the bill adopted by the conference committee in the second chamber, in jurisdictions that do this. Omit if no vote was taken.", "type": "number" }, "veto_override2_abstention": { "label": "Votes to abstain (veto override; second chamber)", "description": "How many members voted to abstain (however called in the jurisdiction; e.g. 'present', 'blank vote') at the vote on overriding the bill's veto in the second chamber. Omit if no vote was taken.", "type": "number" }, "1st_reading2_absent": { "label": "Members absent (first reading; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were absent from the vote in the bill's first reading in the second chamber. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "2nd_reading2_absent": { "label": "Members absent (second reading; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were absent from the vote in the bill's second reading in the second chamber. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "3rd_reading2_absent": { "label": "Members absent (third reading; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were absent from the vote in the bill's third reading in the second chamber. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "passed2_absent": { "label": "Members absent (passage without three readings; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were absent from the vote on the bill's passage in the second chamber, if that chamber does not pass bills in three readings.", "type": "number" }, "conf_committee_passed2_absent": { "label": "Members absent (conference committee; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were absent from the vote on the version of the bill adopted by the conference committee in the second chamber, in jurisdictions that do this. Omit if no vote was taken.", "type": "number" }, "veto_override2_absent": { "label": "Members absent (veto override; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were absent from the vote on overriding the bill's veto in the second chamber. Omit if no vote was taken.", "type": "number" }, "1st_reading2_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but not voting (first reading; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were present at the vote in the bill's first reading in the second chamber, but did not cast a vote. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "2nd_reading2_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but not voting (second reading; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were present at the vote in the bill's second reading in the second chamber, but did not cast a vote. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "3rd_reading2_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but not voting (third reading; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were present at the vote in the bill's third reading in the second chamber, but did not cast a vote. Omit if no vote was taken, or if votes were only taken on amendments.", "type": "number" }, "passed2_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but not voting (passage without three readings; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were present at the vote on the bill's passage in the second chamber, but did not cast a vote, if that chamber does not pass bills in three readings.", "type": "number" }, "conf_committee_passed2_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but not voting (conference committee; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were present at the vote on the version of the bill adopted by the conference committee in the second chamber, in jurisdictions that do this, but did not cast a vote. Omit if no vote was taken.", "type": "number" }, "veto_override2_presentnotvoting": { "label": "Members present but not voting (veto override; second chamber)", "description": "How many members were present at the vote on overriding the bill's veto in the second chamber, but did not cast a vote. Omit if no vote was taken.", "type": "number" }, "codification_affects": { "label": "Acts affected by codification", "type": "content" }, "codification_repeals": { "label": "Acts repealed by codification", "type": "content" }, "code_titles_affected": { "label": "Code titles affected", "type": "content" }, "code_titles_amended": { "label": "Code titles amended", "type": "content" }, "code_sections_created": { "label": "Code sections created", "type": "content" }, "code_sections_affected": { "label": "Code sections affected", "type": "content" }, "code_sections_amended": { "label": "Code sections amended", "type": "content" }, "codification_amends": { "label": "Acts amended by codification", "type": "content" }, "code": { "label": "Name of code affected", "type": "content" }, "code_section_name": { "label": "Divisions of code affected", "description": "The name used for the \"base-unit\" for the Code's provisions. Leave blank if the jurisdiction calls these \"section\".", "type": "string", "suggestedvalues": [ "Article", "Clause" ] }, "authorizing_legislation": { "label": "Authorizing legislation", "description": "For secondary legislation (e.g. regulations, rules, statutory instruments), the legislation that authorizes the making/enactment of this legislation.", "example": "[[Transport Integration Act 2010]]", "type": "content" }, "bill_history_url": { "label": "Bill history webpage", "description": "URL of the webpage on the legislature's website (or equivalent) that shows the legislative history of the bill, if available. Sometimes known as the \"bill homepage\". The \"Legislative history\" heading will be linked to that page.", "example": "https://parlwork.aph.gov.au/bills/r6889", "type": "url", "suggested": true }, "date_introduced2": { "aliases": [ "bill_date2", "introduced_on2" ], "label": "Date bill received from first chamber (second chamber)", "description": "Date when the second chamber received the bill from the first chamber. For bicameral legislatures only.", "type": "date" }, "date_introduced": { "aliases": [ "introduced_on", "bill_date" ], "label": "Date introduced", "description": "Date when the bill was introduced into the legislative chamber specified in 'enacted_by' or 'considered_by'.", "type": "date", "suggested": true } }, "paramOrder": [ "short_title", "legislature", "long_title", "autocollapse_long_title", "citation", "territorial_extent", "considered_by", "enacted_by", "date_passed", "date_enacted", "considered_by2", "enacted_by2", "date_passed2", "date_enacted2", "assented_by", "date_assented", "royal_assent", "signed_by", "date_signed", "vetoed_by", "date_vetoed", "veto_type", "veto_overridden", "reference_holding", "date_pocket_vetoed", "date_became_law_by_inaction", "date_commenced", "date_effective", "date_of_expiry", "date_repealed", "date_abrogated", "authorizing_legislation", "administered_by", "white_paper", "code", "code_section_name", "codification_affects", "codification_amends", "codification_repeals", "code_titles_affected", "code_titles_amended", "code_sections_created", "code_sections_affected", "code_sections_amended", "bill_history_url", "bill", "bill_citation", "introduced_by", "date_introduced", "committee_responsible", "preliminary_reading", "preliminary_reading_for", "preliminary_reading_against", "preliminary_reading_abstention", "preliminary_reading_absent", "preliminary_reading_presentnotvoting", "1st_reading", "1st_reading_for", "1st_reading_against", "1st_reading_abstention", "1st_reading_absent", "1st_reading_presentnotvoting", "committee_post1st", "2nd_reading", "2nd_reading_for", "2nd_reading_against", "2nd_reading_abstention", "2nd_reading_absent", "2nd_reading_presentnotvoting", "committee_post2nd", "committee_whole_label", "committee_whole", "3rd_reading", "3rd_reading_for", "3rd_reading_against", "3rd_reading_abstention", "3rd_reading_absent", "3rd_reading_presentnotvoting", "passed", "passed_for", "passed_against", "passed_abstention", "passed_absent", "passed_presentnotvoting", "committee_report", "bill2", "bill_citation2", "introduced_by2", "date_introduced2", "second_chamber_action", "1st_reading2", "1st_reading2_for", "1st_reading2_against", "1st_reading2_abstention", "1st_reading2_absent", "1st_reading2_presentnotvoting", "committee_post1st2", "2nd_reading2", "2nd_reading2_for", "2nd_reading2_against", "2nd_reading2_abstention", "2nd_reading2_absent", "2nd_reading2_presentnotvoting", "committee_post2nd2", "committee_whole_label2", "committee_whole2", "3rd_reading2", "3rd_reading2_for", "3rd_reading2_against", "3rd_reading2_abstention", "3rd_reading2_absent", "3rd_reading2_presentnotvoting", "passed2", "passed2_for", "passed2_against", "passed2_abstention", "passed2_absent", "passed2_presentnotvoting"